<paragraph id="H83004E07BED145B8916C9A7813629AAC"><enum>(3)</enum><text><quote>State and Local Law Enforcement Activities, Office on Violence Against Women, Violence Against Women Prevention and Prosecution Programs</quote>, $15,000,000;</text> </paragraph> 
