<section commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="H1758F0F462B84DF4B5D1ACE319802B67" section-type="subsequent-section"><enum>8031.</enum><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">During the current fiscal year, appropriations which are available to the Department of Defense for operation and maintenance may be used to purchase items having an investment item unit cost of not more than $250,000.</text> </section> 
<section commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="idBBD8398049FA4CA694DC7AF9BF4E56C9" section-type="subsequent-section"><enum>8032.</enum><text>None of the funds made available by this Act may be used to—</text> 
