<section commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="HAA3E22FAE28B4E3CB5BE32DC47916FC3" section-type="subsequent-section"><enum>8062.</enum><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">Notwithstanding any other provision of law, funds appropriated in this Act under the heading <quote>Research, Development, Test and Evaluation, Defense-Wide</quote> for any new start advanced concept technology demonstration project or joint capability demonstration project may only be obligated 45 days after a report, including a description of the project, the planned acquisition and transition strategy and its estimated annual and total cost, has been provided in writing to the congressional defense committees: 
