<section changed="not-changed" id="H5C2A04B497B84340B9F67FE09379DBD3"><enum>8068.</enum> 
<subsection commented="no" display-inline="yes-display-inline" id="HEE9DE6E7DB2F4ACFBF950177AF518782"><enum>(a)</enum><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">None of the funds appropriated in this or any other Act may be used to take any action to modify—</text> 
<paragraph id="HAB9DD126AB6A4B29A7D3D953C61AC26F"><enum>(1)</enum><text>the appropriations account structure for the National Intelligence Program budget, including through the creation of a new appropriation or new appropriation account;</text> </paragraph> 
