<proviso><italic>Provided further</italic></proviso>, That at least 10 percent shall be allocated for assistance in persistent poverty counties: 
<proviso><italic>Provided further</italic></proviso>, That for purposes of this section, the term <quote>persistent poverty counties</quote> means any county that has had 20 percent or more of its population living in poverty over the past 30 years, as measured by the 1990 and 2000 decennial censuses and the most recent Small Area Income and Poverty Estimates;</text> </paragraph> 
<paragraph id="H227B1A260B8B41979F21FE415B974A33"><enum>(5)</enum><text>$75,000,000 shall be for grants under title VII, subtitle G of the Energy Policy Act of 2005;</text> </paragraph> 
