<proviso><italic>Provided</italic></proviso>, That such funds may only be obligated to carry out construction projects identified in the respective military department’s unfunded priority list for fiscal year 2018 submitted to Congress: 
<proviso><italic>Provided further</italic></proviso>, That such projects are subject to authorization prior to obligation and expenditure of funds to carry out construction: 
