<section id="HF1FE20CF763C4AB99F199458B9090C5A"><enum>126.</enum><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">Of the unobligated balances available to the Department of Defense from prior appropriation Acts, the following funds are hereby rescinded from the following accounts in the amounts specified:</text> 
