<section id="HB7176E9CBC70491DB311D5C00771C8A8"><enum>106.</enum><header>Research, engineering, and development</header><text display-inline="no-display-inline">Section 48102(a)(10) of title 49, United States Code, is amended to read as follows:</text> 
