<section id="HECC39D8AB43A41A18462D8F8E8F2B07D"><enum>14.</enum><header>Small community technical assistance grants</header> 
<subsection id="H9B62494FE83446A799F78D15579E23B9"><enum>(a)</enum><header>In general</header><text>Section 128(a)(1)(B) of the Comprehensive Environmental Response, Compensation, and Liability Act of 1980 (42 U.S.C. 9628(a)(1)(B)) is amended—</text> 
<paragraph id="HFE74AEC9A58A410582E943E20BD48568"><enum>(1)</enum><text>in clause (ii)—</text> 
