<subparagraph id="ide678300ee0734bd2808626724738ff6f"><enum>(C)</enum><header>Elections as to allocation of balance</header><text>Section 102(d)(1) of the Secure Rural Schools and Community Self-Determination Act of 2000 (16 U.S.C. 7112(d)(1)) is amended—</text> 
<clause id="idea4ecc560ab84ba6b6fdcc91812f49d4"><enum>(i)</enum><text>in subparagraph (B)(ii), by striking <quote>not more than 7 percent of the total share for the eligible county of the State payment or the county payment</quote> and inserting <quote>any portion of the balance</quote>; and</text> </clause> 
