<paragraph id="H0B47ABF665EF400694F900BBEFB0EE72"><enum>(2)</enum><text>in section 215—</text> 
<subparagraph id="HC849163137F1416AB1D3407E5BEE5574"><enum>(A)</enum><text>by striking subsection (b); and</text> </subparagraph> 
