<subparagraph id="HCBE3541C3312497D9DA321F3B182CD49"><enum>(C)</enum><text>in paragraph (11), by striking the period at the end and inserting <quote>; and</quote>; and</text> </subparagraph> 
<subparagraph id="H3AA5C9A4147340358F9BF793143712DC"><enum>(D)</enum><text>by inserting after paragraph (11) the following:</text> 
