<paragraph id="id2a84d52930a3481cac2f4d3e61be3964"><enum>(4)</enum><text>in section 2704 (34 U.S.C. 10554)—</text> 
<subparagraph id="id4bd238b907714889a9ddd673ef73abb8"><enum>(A)</enum><text>in paragraph (1)—</text> 
