<paragraph id="H917BADE29B444F079E6839A918B9F29F"><enum>(7)</enum><text>to a foreign government pursuant to an order from a foreign government that is subject to an executive agreement that the Attorney General has determined and certified to Congress satisfies section 2523.</text></paragraph><after-quoted-block>; and</after-quoted-block></quoted-block></subclause></clause></subparagraph> 
